reviews.text: Best Vietnamese food I had in town! Great food with affordable price. Love their Spring rolls

One of the best local viet style restaurants you will find in HK. Unlike the over priced places in central this serves modestly priced delicious viet food that brings back the great memories and taste of Vietnam
Good quality vietnamese food
Great food, great service, very affordable.

We tried the plain noodle soup, cooked beef noodle soup, specialty noodle soup, banh mi, and iced milk tea. Large portions and yummy food!! Quite inexpensive prices for great food. Would recommend trying if you’re in the area!
